data.eml:eml: Genetic relationships of Amaurobioides (Anyphaenidae) spiders from the southeastern coast of New Zealand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Opell, Brent D., Berger, Andrea M., Bous, sophia M., Manning, Michael L. (2007): Genetic relationships of Amaurobioides (Anyphaenidae) spiders from the southeastern coast of New Zealand. Zootaxa 1425: 1-10, URL: http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2007f/zt01425p010.pdf
